high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the left side of the wooden desk
Pick up the book from the left side of the desk
Look up toward the lamp on the left side of the desk
anns.task_desc: Examine the book under the light of the lamp

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the desk in front of you and to your right.
Pick up the book on the left side of the desk.
Look up at the light over the desk.
anns.task_desc: Examine a book by the light over the desk.

high_descs: Cross the room, hang a left at the bed and walk to the gray container on the floor next to the wooden desk.
Pick up the book from the back left corner of the desk.
Look up at the top shelf of the desk to reach the small lamp on the far left corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a book by the light of a small lamp.
